data.description: This is It New Home for the New Year! Sought After Chelford Community In W Viera! Beautiful Single story home on spacious water view lot. Move in ready 4 BR/3BA/3 car garage home features open floor plan w/spacious kitchen, granite counters, large breakfast bar & center island +kitchen nook, 42' cabinet w/crown molding & stainless appliances. Addtl Features include paver driveway, upgraded stonework elevation, bay window in dining room, tank-less gas water heater, built in murphy-bed in front room, tile thru-out living area & LVP in 2 bedrooms. Entertain in Formal dining room +living room opens to patio overlooking water. Great location walking, biking & golf-carting distance to schools, shopping & restaurants. Watch the Rockets go off in your back yard! Enjoy all Viera has to offer.
